  <title>
    Read screen aloud
  </title>

  <p>
    GNOME provides the <app>Orca</app> screen reader to speak the user 
    interface. Depending on how you installed GNOME, you might not have Orca 
    installed. <link href="apt:gnome-orca">Install Orca</link>, and then refer to 
    the <link href="help:gnome-orca">Orca Help</link> for more information.
  </p>

